migid "background_career_banzai.Description.Details"
migstr "Team Banzai has the nicest toys.  <b><color=#ff9900>Quirk: Gladiator, Neural Implants & Pain Shunt. Random Hatchetman</color></b>"
migid "background_career_banzai.Description.Name"
migstr "Testpilot"
migid "background_career_banzai.OptionDescription"
migstr "Tired of living under the authority of others, you fell in with a local pirate gang in the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreRimwardPeriphery],Rimward Periphery]]. It was an unruly crew, but an effective one - roaming the Periphery afforded your outfit with a steady supply of poorly defended merchant caravans and supply depots to prey upon. While raids did occasionally devolve into combat, you quickly learned that successful piracy is mostly about being in the right place, at the right time, with the right threats and a good show of force.

+1 [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[StatMechWarriorGuts],Guts]]"
migid "background_career_banzai.OptionName"
migstr "Testpilot"
migid "background_career_banzai.BioDescription"
migstr "After Years of working for Dr. Banzai you have stuck out on your own and been given one of the Companys treasured Hatchetmen for exceptional service.
"
migid "background_career_freelancer.Description.Details"
migstr "Someone always needs some Work done. <b><color=#ff9900>Quirk: Reckless&Drunk. Mech: Random Hunchback</color></b>"
migid "background_career_freelancer.Description.Name"
migstr "Freelancer"
migid "background_career_freelancer.OptionDescription"
migstr "You roamed the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreRimwardPeriphery],Rimward Periphery]] as a freelancer, signing on for whatever odd contracts you could find as a MechWarrior for hire. It was a solitary life - but as you became more comfortable with the itinerant lifestyle, you found you were able to make a decent living helping the people of the frontier.

+1 [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[StatMechWarriorTactics],Tactics]]"
migid "background_career_freelancer.OptionName"
migstr "Freelancer"
migid "background_career_freelancer.BioDescription"
migstr "Desperate to escape your past, you roamed the Rimward Periphery as a freelancer, signing on for whatever odd contracts you could find as a MechWarrior for hire. It was a solitary life - but as you became more comfortable with the itinerant lifestyle, you found you were able to make a decent living helping the people of the frontier.
"
migid "background_career_gladiator.Description.Details"
migstr "A [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSolaris7],Solaris]] Gladiator. Living for the Spectacle!.  <b><color=#ff9900>Quirk: Gladiator&Honest. Gladitorial Gear.</color></b>"
migid "background_career_gladiator.Description.Name"
migstr "Gladiator"
migid "background_career_gladiator.OptionDescription"
migstr "You took your skills as a MechWarrior to the famed arena planet of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSolaris7],Solaris VII]]. There, you eked out a living as a gladiator, fighting for the crowd in minor arenas, getting by from paycheck to paycheck.

+1 [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[StatMechWarriorGunnery],Gunnery]]"
migid "background_career_gladiator.OptionName"
migstr "Gladiator"
migid "background_career_gladiator.BioDescription"
migstr "Eager to escape your past, you took your Blackjack and your skills as a MechWarrior to the famed arena planet of Solaris VII. There, you eked out a living as a gladiator, fighting for the crowd in minor arenas, getting by from paycheck to paycheck.
"
migid "background_career_infantry.Description.Details"
migstr "Trained as a Battle Armour Pilot, War always bring a Paycheck.  <b><color=#ff9900>Quirk: Dependable&Brave. Spare BA suit and Weapons.</color></b>"
migid "background_career_infantry.Description.Name"
migstr "BA Pilot"
migid "background_career_infantry.OptionDescription"
migstr "Unsure of your prospects, you traveled to [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreCoromodir],Coromodir]], the capital of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAuriganCoalition],Aurigan Coalition]], and enlisted in the Coalition military. You quickly rose through the ranks, distinguishing yourself as a reliable MechWarrior. Life as a soldier wasn't glamorous, but it suited you just fine.

+1 [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[StatMechWarriorGunnery],Gunnery]]"
migid "background_career_infantry.OptionName"
migstr "BA Pilot"
migid "background_career_infantry.BioDescription"
migstr "Unsure of your prospects, you traveled to Coromodir, the capital of the Aurigan Coalition, and enlisted in the Coalition military. You quickly rose through the ranks, distinguishing yourself as a reliable MechWarrior. Life as a soldier wasn't glamorous, but it suited you just fine.
"
migid "background_career_inheritor.Description.Details"
migstr "It belonged in a museum but now it's yours.  <b><color=#ff9900>Quirk: Lucky&Noble. Mech: Random Rare Mech.</color></b>"
migid "background_career_inheritor.Description.Name"
migstr "Inheritor"
migid "background_career_inheritor.OptionDescription"
migstr "It may have been years since you last spoke to your great-uncle but you must have left an impression or you were simply the only one left in the family. While his passing didn't leave you with his money; it did leave you with some information on his business contacts, his prized 'Mech freshly pulled out of mothballs, and a request to make a name for yourself."
migid "background_career_inheritor.OptionName"
migstr "Inheritor"
migid "background_career_inheritor.BioDescription"
migstr "You took to plying yourself as a mercenary and found yourself traveling the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreInnerSphere],Inner Sphere]]. While you're not the best pilot, you've been lucky enough to make it this far and a gift from a distant relative might prove to be the break you were looking for. 
"
migid "background_career_mercenary.Description.Details"
migstr "A [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreInnerSphere],Inner Sphere]] Mercenary. War does Pay Well.  <b><color=#ff9900>Quirk: Athletic&Mechwarrior. Random Advanced Unit.</color></b>"
migid "background_career_mercenary.Description.Name"
migstr "Mercenary"
migid "background_career_mercenary.OptionDescription"
migstr "Eager to get away from it all, you joined up with a minor [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreInnerSphere],Inner Sphere]] mercenary unit. Integrating into the tight-knit crew took time, but you eventually proved your worth and became part of the family.

+1 [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[StatMechWarriorTactics],Tactics]]"
migid "background_career_mercenary.OptionName"
migstr "Mercenary"
migid "background_career_mercenary.BioDescription"
migstr "Eager to get away from your past and make a name for yourself, you joined up with a minor Inner Sphere mercenary unit. Integrating into the tight-knit crew took time, but you eventually proved your worth and became part of the family.
